org.locationtech.geowave.core.geotime.index.dimension

Class LatitudeDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.locationtech.geowave.core.index.dimension.BasicDimensionDefinition
      • org.locationtech.geowave.core.geotime.index.dimension.LatitudeDefinition
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NumericDimensionDefinition, Persistable

    public class LatitudeDefinition
extends BasicDimensionDefinition
    The Latitude Definition class is a convenience class used to define a dimension which is associated with the Y axis on a Cartesian plane.

    Minimum bounds = -90 and maximum bounds = 90
